social_posts.post_text: Well this one’s bittersweet but a little announcement that our boy @adamobrien_art is leaving us next month to go see how he likes being a Texan for a while… Its been a great time working with him these past few years, he’s been an honest, fun, funny, hard worker and it’s been truly inspiring to watch him grow so much so fast with us. We wish you all the luck in the world Adam and hope to see you again! —— This also means we will have a full time opening for a new artist @the.great.wave.sd so let’s get that ball rolling. For inquiries email myself or Charlie I’m excited to find out who might get that spot! We love you Adam!! 💕
“I’m not crying, it’s just been raining… on my face” 🥹
Big thanks to my bestie @scxtty.ftw for all the trust on this one. A lot of winding and weaving but we got it and I’m very happy with it
An oldie from 2016 reminded me of a psa I had for everybody… Quit fuckin around and get a backpiece @the.great.wave.sd
Healed shots!  Anyone else having these turn darker than your actual video by quite a bit? I even turned up the brightness on this one 🤔 they always be changing’ shit @the.great.wave.sd
Started with the ribs around 2012… one of my favorite people to see in the shop @_catchin_playz__ thanks for always being a good hang #tattoo
Can you see yourself with a tattoo like this? It’s not an easy thing but in the end it’s one of the best things you could ever do for yourself @the.great.wave.sd @scxtty.ftw
Fun fun fun! Freehand writing throughout by the legend @scxtty.ftw 🙏🏼@the.great.wave.sd
Make sure you’re following @the.great.wave.sd there’s exciting stuff happening daily with this crew!

Snuck a lil scuba in on you guys in there, pulled a lil sneaky on ya ____________________________________
